channel.title: Comments on: Depeche Mode cause frenzy on Hollywood Boulevard

item.title: By: K
item.dc:creator: K
item.description: Yeah, his voice is impressive. I just felt that arrangement was a bit thin. I think of PJ as a stadium rocker. Big and full and overpowering.
item.content:encoded: Yeah, his voice is impressive. I just felt that arrangement was a bit thin. I think of PJ as a stadium rocker. Big and full and overpowering.

item.title: By: Eric Greenwood
item.dc:creator: Eric Greenwood
item.description: really? i thought it was a cool arrangement. and dave gahan's voice always sounds great live.
item.content:encoded: really? i thought it was a cool arrangement. and dave gahan’s voice always sounds great live.

item.title: By: K
item.dc:creator: K
item.description: Man. That really looks like it would have been a lot of fun! (Though, that version of Personal Jesus wasn't all that impressive.)
